#

Sriracha Lime Burger

25 min
$12
550 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Wheat

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

QuickSpicyGrilled

Description

A juicy burger with a spicy kick from sriracha and a zesty lime twist, perfect for a quick and flavorful meal!

Ingredients

  • ground beef (80% lean): 1 lb
  • sriracha sauce: 2 tbsp
  • lime juice: 1 tbsp
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • salt: 1 tsp
  • pepper: 1/2 tsp
  • burger buns: 4
  • lettuce: 4 leaves
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • cheddar cheese (optional): 4 slices
